    }
  },
  ">>The zombies have 5 seconds left to start pursuing<<": {
    "translation": ">>僵尸5秒钟后可以开始追击<<",
    "MultiLang": {
      "US": "",
      "JP": ">>ゾンビの追跡開始まで残り5秒です<<",
